<section id="challenges" class="py-18">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-normal font-[Industry] text-pale-turquoise mb-12">
      > Repetitive Tasks Are Draining Your Startup's Potential_
    </h2>
    <div class="py-5 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/timer.png"
            alt="timer"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-4 text-center">
          Wasted Hours & Spiraling Costs
        </h3>

        <p class="font-light mb-4">
          Spending countless hours on manual data entry, repetitive reporting,
          or moving information between disconnected apps? This isn't just time
          lost; it's focus diverted and resources drained.
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium">
          Imagine reclaiming those hours, reducing operational costs, and
          empowering your team to focus on innovation and growth. This is the
          power of smart automation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
        <!-- <img
          width="56"
