        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/services.png"
            alt="services"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-4 text-center">
          Inconsistent Processes & Costly Errors
        </h3>
        <p class="font-light mb-4">
          Are manual steps leading to human errors, inconsistent customer
          experiences, or vital tasks falling through the cracks? These slip-ups
          can damage reputation and impact your bottom line.
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium">
          Picture streamlined, error-free operations where every process runs
          consistently, ensuring quality and reliability for your customers and
          internal teams.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/network.png"
            alt="network"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-4 text-center">
          Disconnected Systems & Data Silos
        </h3>
        <p class="font-light mb-4">
          Struggling with data that lives in isolated apps? This makes it hard
          to get a clear view of your business and forces time-consuming manual
          reconciliation.
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium">
          Envision a connected ecosystem where your essential tools communicate
          seamlessly, providing you with real-time insights and a single source
          of truth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

